{"tid":2013512,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"寬頻上網插lan線速度","createTime":"2020-05-12T10:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T10:48:23.000Z","uid":144999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"118580e06240babeb2dcc1cc0fe242bbb01859e4","tid":2013512,"uid":144999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:46:16.000Z","msg":"而家情況係咁<br />\n網絡供應商：Netvigator 1000 mbps <br />\nRouter: Asus ac68u （cat 5e線）<br />\nLan卡：Realtek PCIe GBE Family Controller (GBE= max 1000mbps)<br />\nWireless Internet Card: Intel(R) Dual Band Wireless-AC 3165 (max. 433.3 mbps)<br />\nLan 線: Cat 6 <br />\n<br />\n駁法：Modem&mdash;&mdash;Router&mdash;&mdash;電腦<br />\n（不能Modem&mdash;&mdash;電腦，因為得一個IP)<br />\n<br />\n速度：<br />\n1. iPad連wifi 有450 mbps<br />\n2. 電腦連wifi 有100-180 mbps (可能電腦張無線卡渣？）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 電腦插lan線得180-190 mbps (上唔到200 mbps)</span><br />\n<br />\n試左兩條lan 線都係寫1.0 Gbps，都試過router同電腦線互換，結果都一樣。我諗得兩個可能，一係電腦張卡壞壞地，一係網上行出事，我已經打左去問，佢話會幫我查下，呢兩日會覆我，但我心急想快啲知咩事，係咪個師傅裝錯左。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人試過咁樣?"},{"pid":"1704a7f29ba5860b78a09c112f0a22363f1a3833","tid":2013512,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:04:35.000Z","msg":"得一個Ip點解唔可以直接用modem連電腦？"},{"pid":"d6ee140d4a9de67b22fddeeb138870bd69b94376","tid":2013512,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:06:08.000Z","msg":"可能係你電腦個Lan Card唔Support 1000Mbs，因為你Ipad都有400幾500"},{"pid":"451fbd8808ec2b1028c8316b407c8d38c5328841","tid":2013512,"uid":144999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1704a7f29ba5860b78a09c112f0a22363f1a3833","tid":2013512,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:04:35.000Z","msg":"得一個Ip點解唔可以直接用modem連電腦？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:51:20.000Z","msg":"個ip俾左router"},{"pid":"388f8416287578b8b48e8cf6ed0275399d36986c","tid":2013512,"uid":144999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6ee140d4a9de67b22fddeeb138870bd69b94376","t